# All providers (Cursor + Antigravity)

- Machine rules in `AGENTS.md` and `workflow/CONSCIOUS.md` apply to **Cursor, Antigravity, and any other AI agent**.
- `.cursor/rules` and `.cursor/skills` do not limit scope to Cursor only — other providers must follow the same CONSCIOUS orders.
- Activity log, promote evidence, and **docs-after-action** (CONSCIOUS #12) are required regardless of provider.
- Antigravity sessions: read `AGENTS.md` first; log to `workflow/activity/ACTIVITY-LOG.md` with provider `antigravity`.
